Quick and dirty guide to our Website
====================================

- checkout our repository in Git called "web".

- change/add stuff there 

- commit and push changes to Git

-create interactive shell session (see http://sourceforge.net/apps/trac/sourceforge/wiki/Shell%20service):
 ssh -t USER,xu4@shell.sourceforge.net create

- change dir to our webspace (cd /home/project-web/xu4/web)

- execute "./update.sh" (updates /home/project-web/xu4/web with Git version and gives the right permissions to everyone)

Please make use of this and do not edit the webspace directly.
